      "text": "我不想听不想再听",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 71.65,
      "time_str": "01:11.650",
      "text": "就把一切誓言当作气球一般随它而去",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 75.03,
      "time_str": "01:15.030",
      "text": "我不在意不会在意",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 76.77,
      "time_str": "01:16.770",
      "text": "放它而去随它而去",
      "translation": null
    },
